{"tid":957709,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【的士無優惠　阿嬸嗌投訴　司機全程淡淡定】","createTime":"2018-12-27T08:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T11:46:48.000Z","uid":225464,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6f7afed50ccadf7a779e2f365c721d5adcff459c","tid":957709,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T08:42:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181227/bkn-20181227154706397-1227_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181227%2Fbkn-20181227154706397-1227_00822_001.html&d=idkdSC%2BxPlwqqHT1giX9GqS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=0ed07899\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181227/bkn-20181227154706397-1227_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a3t52WU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa3t52WU.jpg&h=e75d85ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>的士無優惠　醉娃嗌投訴　司機全程淡淡定</strong><br />\n<br />\n聖誕狂歡是人之常情，但如樂極忘形，隨時鬧出笑話。近日馬鞍山有婦人疑因醉酒，與的士司機就車資問題發生爭執，更勞動警察到場解決。<br />\n<br />\n從Facebook群組「香港交通突發報料區」的影片可見，周三（26日）凌晨2時許，馬鞍山寧泰路有一名看似醉醺醺的婦人，在的士上口齒不清地與司機爭辯，期間婦人一直以手機與警察通話。<br />\n<br />\n該婦人向司機表示：「你找錢畀我嗎，因為差人問我&hellip;你嗱嗱聲找啦，唔係我走唔到」、「問題我call九折的喎，我七八五折的㗎喎，你係咪唔算，唔算我就投訴你啦」。司機耐心地回應：「冇問題，你投訴我唔畀折頭你啦」。<br />\n<br />\n婦人落車後情緒仍然激動，有兩名警察到場了解，着司機可自行離去︰「往後嘅嘢我哋做啦，純粹醉酒人士啫，我哋睇吓有冇需要送佢返屋企」。<br />\n<br />\n不少網友嘲諷婦人：「傻人發現案」、「唔飲得唔好飲啦」，又稱讚司機：「好好禮貌」、「處理得幾好」。"},{"pid":"48dee92867fc831e6e2db0777df84372838e6c0f","tid":957709,"uid":18587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T08:58:01.000Z","msg":"投訴無折<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9ef0e47969aa43c6c0f55afa20af55242b7889","tid":957709,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T09:25:12.000Z","msg":"可能冇兩蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b2374823f277e892295755a2d9bde0be22d5f03","tid":957709,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T10:32:16.000Z","msg":"究竟係九折定七五折？"},{"pid":"5bc8db5331446d2e6d8aa1f586fc1b5074d450c3","tid":957709,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:26:39.000Z","msg":"咦 的士點解會有折嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51317da7d11271d5f9aaa3ed29a09dbdb5113307","tid":957709,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bc8db5331446d2e6d8aa1f586fc1b5074d450c3","tid":957709,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:26:39.000Z","msg":"咦 的士點解會有折嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T11:46:48.000Z","msg":"如果佢真係經電話/call車app嘅，有折唔出奇。<br />\n但係睇佢嘅對答，究竟佢有冇咁做都成問題。"}]}